{"tid":2254151,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"壁虎脫皮(求救)","createTime":"2020-10-22T15:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T12:06:58.000Z","uid":84394,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f7db9f836a84af4e375548af4f9e9cd83137a6d7","tid":2254151,"uid":84394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:21:03.000Z","msg":"突然發現屋企有隻脫緊皮既壁虎係廁所地下<br />\n佢脫左一半皮又脫唔到一半咁<br />\n但又好似爬唔到上牆<br />\n因為聽人講脫唔到皮既壁虎可能會死<br />\n又驚有人踩死佢<br />\n所以依家搵個地方比佢脫皮先，之後再方返走。<br />\n但除左比佢環境濕潤啲外，仲有咩方法可以幫佢?<br />\n有咩野食可以容易取得又比到佢?<br />\n好驚佢死呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23bd9584c625b5d3e7a1b8cb7a0911a8f2d8a009","tid":2254151,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:24:55.000Z","msg":"帶佢睇獸醫囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完記得放生啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0dfc3c72c6fbef04aa91c984b591e8a7f3adcb","tid":2254151,"uid":84394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23bd9584c625b5d3e7a1b8cb7a0911a8f2d8a009","tid":2254151,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:24:55.000Z","msg":"帶佢睇獸醫囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完記得放生啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:28:15.000Z","msg":"有無連燈獸醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b38c88276c70f3b1778a77a8d1248846f2e423","tid":2254151,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:29:54.000Z","msg":"噴水 擺d甜野食比佢 啫喱<br />\n或者用鉗幫佢拉d死皮"},{"pid":"aeef243d9c932ad56a9333a357173cc071c81683","tid":2254151,"uid":84394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56b38c88276c70f3b1778a77a8d1248846f2e423","tid":2254151,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020